&lt;li&gt;Own Niche&#39;s organic social strategy across B2C and B2B channels, developing and implementing platform-specific approaches that grow our brand and move our business forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Head of Content to align social with broader content, brand, and business goals to ensure social is integrated into campaigns, product launches, partner building strategies, and key company moments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and lead our ambassador, influencer, and community strategies: identifying the right partners, managing contracts, budgets, and briefs, and building ongoing connections with key audiences across platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor emerging channels, audience behaviors, new platform features, and algorithm changes to make proactive recommendations on where and how Niche should show up next&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
